"""
Hoster CLI — Payload Hosting Tool

Modes:
  hoster ui                   → Interactive TUI (requires: pip install rich questionary)
  hoster <command> [args]     → Classic CLI mode

Commands:
  setup       Configure the client
  up          Upload a file or inline content  (--watch to auto-re-upload on change)
  ls          List routes
  rm          Delete a route
  edit        Edit a route
  clone       Clone a route
  tag         Add a tag to a route
  untag       Remove a tag from a route
  test        Test a route (HTTP request)
  cors        Configure CORS on a route
  headers     Configure custom response headers on a route
  export      Export all routes to JSON
  import      Import routes from JSON
  logs        Watch access logs live  ([route] to filter by route)
  url         Get the URL of a route
  open        Open route URL in the default browser
  completion  Print shell completion script (bash/zsh)
"""

